history.content: Online CS courses cannot be transferred for credit, in general. If anyone has an option, feel free to chime in but the chances are highly unlikely. In fact, Berkeley's own CS 169 is offered as a MOOC through edX over the summer yet credits for it cannot be transferred over to here.

Does anyone know any online cs class offered now or in the summer that can fulfill the upper division CS course requirement here at Berkeley?

 

A CS advisor said I am welcome to find one, but she does not know of any. It must be something equivalent to what is taught here and upper division.
history.subject: Online upper division course?
